name: Skydive Over Airlie Beach And the Whitsundays!
description: Experience the thrill of a lifetime with Skydive Airlie Beach, where adventure meets stunning natural beauty. This skydive offers breathtaking views of the Great Barrier Reef and the Whitsunday Islands, making it a unique experience for thrill-seekers and nature lovers alike. Perfect for adrenaline junkies, the skydive promises an exhilarating freefall and a scenic descent over turquoise waters and lush islands. Whether you're a seasoned skydiver or a first-timer, this adventure is sure to leave you with unforgettable memories and a sense of accomplishment.
departure_location: Whitsunday Airport, Air Whitsunday Road, Whitsunday Airport, Flame Tree, QLD 4802
includes:
Tandem skydive from up to 8,000ft or 15,000ft
Up to 60 seconds of freefall
Personalised certificate of achievement
Compulsory Personal Accident Insurance from the Australian Parachute Federation
3 month membership of the Australian Parachute Federation
highlights:
Spectacular views of the Great Barrier Reef
Breathtaking descent over the Whitsunday Islands
Convenient location with no long transfers
Capture your experience with high-resolution video packages
Free transfers from selected spots around Airlie Beach
price_tiers: Tandem Skydive 8,000ft: FROM A$309 | Tandem Skydive 15,000ft: FROM A$369
locations: Airlie Beach,Great Barrier Reef,Hamilton Island,Whitsunday Island
ideal_for: Adrenaline junkies, first-time skydivers, nature lovers, and adventure seekers
